      "description": "Well-kept good-condition driver that should suit someone wanting a car they can enjoy right away without paying top dollar for a fully restored example. It presents nicely overall, with solid paint, tidy interior, and a clean, cared-for appearance, though you should still expect some normal age-related wear and minor cosmetic imperfections on close inspection. A strong, honest car that feels more sorted than a project or average driver, and one a buyer can use and improve over time if desired.",
